attributes.description:
The following account(s) need to be termed in the William Hill domain:

•	Employee Number: {{$.getIdentity.attributes.personNumber}}
•	Employee Name: {{$.getIdentity.name}}
•	Primary Location: {{$.getIdentity.attributes.locationDescription}}
•	Primary Job Title: {{$.getIdentity.attributes.jobTitle}}
•	Primary Department: {{$.getIdentity.attributes.department}}
•	AD Source Name: CZR-Application-ActiveDirectory-WilliamHill
•	Network ID: {{$.getAccounts.accounts[?(@.sourceName== 'CZR-Application-ActiveDirectory-Dev.lab.local')].attributes.sAMAccountName}}
•	Termination Date: {{$.getIdentity.attributes.terminationDate}}

The following company phones need to be locked for this terminated user.

•	Employee Number: {{$.getIdentity.attributes.personNumber}}
•	Employee Name: {{$.getIdentity.name}}
•	Company Phone: {{$.getAccounts.accounts[?(@.sourceName== 'CZR-Application-MobileDevice')].attributes.Number}}
